  Book your Private Eventwith Clink




  We would love to bring good food, drink and cheer to your special event. Clink is proud to offer both the best and the basics in food, beer, wine and spirits. If you want something specific, just ask —  we will do everything we can to find and offer it for you. We also offer a variety of non-alcoholic options on draft and in bottles and cans.

